tps:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/24095118\/multipurpose-bench-small-balcony-decoration-india-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/24095118\/multipurpose-bench-small-balcony-decoration-india-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A multifunctional storage bench on a small balcony <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Leverage The Floor For Simple Balcony Decoration<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seating arrangements do not always have to be about tables and chairs. A floor seating arrangement with the help of pouffes or large cushions can make your balcony the perfect place to unwind. Add a rug for comfortable seating and a tall mirror to make the balcony look more spacious. If your balcony opens up to a great view, place the mirror to reflect the view and enhance the beauty of your balcony.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/24095136\/small-balcony-decor-with-seating-arrangements.jpg\" alt=\"Small balcony decored with floor seating with the help of poufs or large cushions\" class=\"wp-image-39566\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/24095136\/small-balcony-decor-with-seating-arrangements.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/24095136\/small-balcony-decor-with-seating-arrangements-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/24095136\/small-balcony-decor-with-seating-arrangements-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/24095136\/small-balcony-decor-with-seating-arrangements-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Vibrant floor seating for a balcony with a boho vibe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a